title: $:/plugins/rimir/kind/changelog
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

! Changelog

|!Version |!Date |!Changes |
|v0.1.84 |2026-07-14 |The graph tooltip's node actions are now reusable outside the graph. Extracted the modal-driving actions into shared engine procedures (`kind.gm-edit` / `kind.gm-delete` / `kind.gm-add-child`) and added a self-contained `$:/plugins/rimir/kind/entity-actions` tiddler that renders the //edit// + //Add child// cluster for any instance (reads `ea-entity` from scope). The //Instances Overview// tooltip now uses these procedures too (no behaviour change); [[rimir/dashboard|$:/plugins/rimir/dashboard]] uses `entity-actions` to offer entity edit / add-child on kind-instance tiles. |
|v0.1.83 |2026-07-14 |''Instances Overview'' layout: the ''Edges'' controls now sit on their own row (own `.kg-controls` block) instead of trailing the search row, matching the ''Types'' row. |
|v0.1.82 |2026-07-14 |''Instances Overview'' search gains a ''keep view & highlight'' mode: instead of shrinking the graph to just the matches and refitting (still the default), it holds the current zoom/pan and greys out non-matches so you can see //where// matches sit in the whole picture (persisted to `$:/config/rimir/kind/instances-overview/search-mode`). Added a clear (✕) button next to the search box. Search wiring now lives in the shared `kg-graph` renderer (new `searchText`/`searchMode` params), so the Context preview is unaffected. |
|v0.1.81 |2026-07-08 |New per-kind story-river cockpit ViewTemplates: ''person-view'' (instances referencing the person, grouped/ranked, with role + status filters) and ''conversation-view'' (Participants · editable Minutes · Notes). Shared notes/content helpers moved from `palette/preview/notes.tid` into `engine.tid`. |
|v0.1.80 |2026-07-08 |Story-river kind-type picker: click the field-bar type icon to change/remove the type; untyped tiddlers get an optional ''＋ type'' assign dropdown (settings toggle + qualifying filter). Fixes: single-value fields with spaces no longer split on a comma in the bar; popup field editor now autofocuses (and inline-mode validation now engages). |
|v0.1.79 |2026-06-15 |Fix: cascade-palette rows whose caption / title / value contained a `"` (or `\`) silently vanished — hand-built row JSON now escapes embedded display text (`kind.json-escape`, routed through `kind.kv`). |
|v0.1.78 |2026-06-11 |//Notes// side-preview: related list restricted to configured note-kinds (`$:/config/rimir/kind/notes-preview/kinds`, default `note`); empty notes get a ''＋'' add-node button and an ''✎ Text'' inline editor. |
|v0.1.77 |2026-06-11 |New //Notes// cascade-palette side-preview: an instance's own content (text + Streams structure) plus every note / child pointing to it, newest-first; Stream / Tabbed layout toggle. (Streams soft-dep.) |
|v0.1.76 |2026-06-11 |Creation wizard: date-step pre-fill (`ca-step-date-default`), force-land-in-optional (`ca-step-auto-edit`), and finish returns to the launching entity. |
|v0.1.75 |2026-06-10 |Creation wizard: per-instance preferred ''spawn-locations'' — ★-pinned quick-pick rows at the top of the parent-picker (new `kind.spawn-locations` common field). |
|v0.1.74 |2026-06-10 |Creation wizard: runtime ⇄ switch between tree and flat parent-picker layouts, remembered per step. |
|v0.1.73 |2026-06-10 |Creation wizard: hands-free step landing, drillable tree parent-picker (pick = create), per-node graph preview, return-to-entity on finish. |
|v0.1.72 |2026-06-10 |Designer-defined multi-step creation wizards — a kind can be created via an ordered guided flow (steps tagged `$:/tags/rimir/kind/wizard-step`) instead of one all-fields form. |
|v0.1.71 |2026-06-09 |Fix: auto-children now reliably inherit their parent — nest `apply-auto-children` inside `$action-createtiddler` + read `<<createTiddler-title>>` (the sibling `$savetitle` read was stale). |
|v0.1.70 |2026-06-09 |Reverse-reference navigation — a "Referenced by…" drill from any instance back to the instances that reference it, grouped per relation with per-kind group/sort config. |
|v0.1.69 |2026-06-09 |Fix: Instances Overview edge selection now persists — renamed the storage field from `fields` (collides with the TiddlyWeb sync wire-format container) to `edges`. |
|v0.1.68 |2026-06-08 |Quick-create drill (subset of fields + derived caption), per-ref ''Manage <field>…'' actions, and a duration / daterange widget. Ref / enum pickers now float selected entries to the top. |
|v0.1.66 |2026-06-04 |Kind icon lens declares `ca-lens-actions: via-entity-type` so Open / Edit / Delete stay available even when the Icon lens slot is off. (cascade-palette ≥0.0.111) |
|v0.1.65 |2026-06-04 |"Kind icons" migrated from structure-toggle to a ''Kind'' icon ''lens'' (Icon slot); same behaviour, off by default. (cascade-palette ≥0.0.110) |
|v0.1.64 |2026-06-04 |Graph tooltip node actions (edit / delete / Add child per accepting kind) + a `graph-modal` overlay, on Instances Overview and Context preview nodes. |
|v0.1.63 |2026-06-03 |Cascade-palette "Kind icons" structure toggle — kind rows show their `kind.icon`; off by default. (cascade-palette ≥0.0.109) |
|v0.1.62 |2026-06-02 |Refactor: `kind.kv` JSON-pair helper + `kind.finalize-create` save-flow consolidation. |
|v0.1.61 |2026-06-02 |Context preview: graph fills the side-preview pane's visible height (no scrolling). |
|v0.1.60 |2026-06-02 |Perf: graph edge colour/stroke computed per-field once, not per-edge. |
|v0.1.59 |2026-06-02 |Context preview: edge + type pills, colour-coded edges; graph + stylesheet fixes. |
|v0.1.58 |2026-06-02 |New: //Context// cascade-palette side-preview + shared graph module. |
|v0.1.57 |2026-06-02 |New: //Kind: Instances Overview// graph view. |
|v0.1.56 |2026-06-02 |Fix: dependent-default cascade didn't re-fire on ref/enum pick in either creator OR cascade-palette. |
|v0.1.55 |2026-05-31 |Unified `default` as a subfilter — dynamic defaults that read from the draft, re-fire after ref/enum changes. |
|v0.1.54 |2026-05-31 |Cascade-palette: structured CRUD drill for `kind.auto-children` — no more JSON typing. |
